---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Testimonials | Belvedere Decks"
  description="What Maryland homeowners say about working with Belvedere Decks: honest inspections, exact same-visit pricing, and a 10-year written workmanship warranty."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Testimonials</p>
      <h1>What homeowners say about working with us.</h1>
      <div class="rule"></div>
      <p class="lead">
        We'd rather show you real words from real customers than write our own praise.
        Reviews land here as each project wraps up.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- TESTIMONIALS: real customer reviews only - name (first name + last initial),
           town, service line, and the review text. Add Google review links as they come in.
           First entries expected from: Hammil (Boyds), Bonaparte. -->
      <div class="notice">
        <strong>Our first projects are under construction right now.</strong> As each one
        finishes, the homeowner's review goes here, in their words, next to the photos of
        their deck. Until then, the honest version: we're a new company, and every early
        customer gets the owner on-site every day, pricing built in front of them, and a
        10-year written workmanship warranty.
      </div>

      <h2>Want to talk to a recent customer?</h2>
      <p>
        Ask during your estimate visit. Once our first projects complete, we're happy to
        connect you with homeowners who agreed to be references.
      </p>

      <p><a class="btn primary" href="/estimate">Get a Free Estimate</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
